title: #108:  Esoteric Hollywood with Jay Dyer
description: Thank you for tuning in for another fantastic episode of Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli.  This episode Sam and Ryan welcome the author of Esoteric Hollywood, Jay Dyer. We discuss the insane world of the Hollywood Occult and the propaganda of the Haunted Brown Eye!  Thank you so much for listening.  We appreciate your support!
